f this summit, because of the G7 summit,", "tokens": [50690, 1436, 295, 341, 21564, 11, 570, 295, 264, 460, 22, 21564, 11, 50861], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1824409997285302, "compression_ratio": 1.5321637426900585, "no_speech_prob": 3.628039535463756e-11}, {"id": 21, "seek": 8194, "start": 92.58, "end": 96.38, "text": " because the EU negotiations for Ukraine started this week,", "tokens": [50897, 570, 264, 10887, 20476, 337, 14081, 1409, 341, 1243, 11, 51087], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1824409997285302, "compression_ratio": 1.5321637426900585, "no_speech_prob": 3.628039535463756e-11}, {"id": 22, "seek": 8194, "start": 96.7, "end": 101.66, "text": " and because of the support that our NATO allies are giving to Ukraine.", "tokens": [51103, 293, 570, 295, 264, 1406, 300, 527, 19419, 14719, 366, 2902, 281, 14081, 13, 51351], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1824409997285302, "compression_ratio": 1.5321637426900585, "no_speech_prob": 3.628039535463756e-11}, {"id": 23, "seek": 10166, "start": 101.66, "end": 108.34, "text": " So I think that Ukraine actually starts this path towards peace from a position of strength", "tokens": [50365, 407, 286, 519, 300, 14081, 767, 3719, 341, 3100, 3030, 4336, 490, 257, 2535, 295, 3800, 50699], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10728095707140471, "compression_ratio": 1.336, "no_speech_prob": 4.405249429129121e-11}, {"id": 24, "seek": 10166, "start": 108.34, "end": 113.94, "text": " much stronger than what it was three weeks ago, let alone three months ago.", "tokens": [50699, 709, 7249, 813, 437, 309, 390, 1045, 3259, 2057, 11, 718, 3312, 1045, 2493, 2057, 13, 50979], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10728095707140471, "compression_ratio": 1.336, "no_speech_prob": 4.405249429129121e-11}, {"id": 25, "seek": 11394, "start": 113.94, "end": 118.7, "text": " My third and final point is, when we talk about peace,", "tokens": [50365, 1222, 2636, 293, 2572, 935, 307, 11, 562, 321, 751, 466, 4336, 11, 50603